python3-libdatovka (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add DatovkaClient.send_message() for sending new messages with
    file attachments, and DatovkaClient.find_box_live() for looking
    up a recipient's data box ID via the live ISDS fulltext search.
  * Add OutgoingDocument model for composing attachments to send.
  * Fix _build_isds_list() passing raw ctypes structs where the C API
    expects pointers, causing send_message() to crash with
    "'IsdsDocument' object cannot be interpreted as ctypes.c_void_p"
    before ever reaching the server. Found by a live send test
    (rejected server-side only by ISDS's own "cannot send to your
    own data box" rule, confirming the envelope/document encoding
    itself is correct).

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Thu, 16 Jul 2026 10:43:27 +0200

python3-libdatovka (0.1.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix DEFAULT_URL missing trailing slash, causing isds_login to
    concatenate the SOAP service path directly onto the hostname
    (e.g. "mojedatovaschranka.czDS/dz") and fail DNS resolution.
    Found by testing against a real ISDS account.

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Thu, 16 Jul 2026 10:07:50 +0200

python3-libdatovka (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging.

